snippet.title: Game Grumps: Joint Justice - Turnabout Power Hour Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Official trailer Trailer for the Parody Video Game "Game Grumps: Joint Justice - Turnabout Power Hour" the first game in the series!

This game has been a project in the making for the past two years by a Lovely team of writers, programmers, artists, composers, and more!
We are all so happy the game is finally out for the rest of the lovelies to play! 

Are you interested in our team, and maybe want to help make the next chapter? Or just want to hang out with us? 
join our community Discord here: https://discord.gg/QFNWXD33YW

Download the game through our website
https://www.studiolovelies.com/projects
or through the discord!

The first song: https://youtu.be/EukbnvmhSQ4

The second song: https://youtu.be/VqbJz5tb-kw

Thanks to KodaOfPlanetEarth for making this trailer! 
Check them out here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkLVjzsiABeOXHZpGKS5ySg
